	function F = FACTORIAL(n)	% 	Computes the factorial, n! = Gamma(n+1) of an integer, 	% 	where Gamma is the well-known gamma function	%	% 	Toolbox for DIGITAL FILTERS USING MATLAB 		% 	Author: 		Lars Wanhammar, 2004-07-15	% 	Modified by: 	LW 2017-03-18 	% 	Copyright:		by authors - not released for commercial use	% 	Version: 		1	% 	Known bugs:		 	% 	Report bugs to:	Wanhammar@gmail.com			F = prod(1:n);	% if n == 0	% 	F = 1;	% else	% 	F = n*FACTORIAL(n-1);	% end	